 If your server allows for 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

PUT
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 at a specific set of URIs, then they are likewise part of your URI-space.
 In other words, you 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

support
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

