\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

/user/profile/
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 URI.
 Within your 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

profile.s.html
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 file, you could then access the captured value as 
\bar under
conversation.locals (page 
