\begin_layout Subsubsection
Dynamic Capturing
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
URI capturing can actually do more than just capture to a 
\emph on
single
\emph default
 URI: the target URI for a capture is, in fact, 
\emph on
also
\emph default
