\end_inset

 after them, so it will catch whatever doesn't have the special 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

.m.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

.s.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 pre-extensions:
