rence)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Our filter doesn't do much yet, but it's easy to test that the code is being
 called by looking at the log.
 Of course you can do many other things here, as detailed in the examples
