\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand pageref
reference "cookies"

\end_inset

)
\bar default
 is used with a magic value.
 It can be used to make sure that certain resources are unavailable for
 users who are not administrators:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
