 Because host files are executed in alphabetical order, a good way to ensure
 that the hungry host is last is to number your host filenames.
 For example:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
1-public.js
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
2-private.js
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
3-default.js (this is the hungry host)
\end_layout

